PrecisOrder authorizing the trip undertaken by several Members of Parliament, namely Mr. IAIN F. ANGUS, Mrs. GABRIELLE BERTRAND, Mr. MURRAY DORIN and the Hon. ROY MacLAREN, from July 1 to July 10, 1992, for the purpose of accompanying the Minister for International Trade on his trip to Russia, the Ukraine and Kazakhstan, in order to promote trade between Canada and the new countries formed by the restructuring of the former U.S.S.R.
